profile_positions.description:
Conducted detailed reviews and analysis of data sources to support the incorporation of gender and social inclusion issues in Land tenure and ICT (Togo) programme design of  MCC Threshhold Programs;  
Facilitated Stakeholder consultations, stakeholder & political economy analysis, social inclusion & gender analysis, to identify issues& inform solutions for program design with high level of stakeholder buy-in;
Liaised with government counterparts to develop feasible project design in line with national agricultural development, decentralisation and social development strategies and MCC Priorities
Provided technical input to program design, feasibility studies, social and gender integration plans  and performance monitoring and evaluation approaches. 

Lead national technical team & working groups to develop National Programme for Local Governance;
Contributed to strengthening UNDP country office strategic engagement in governance & decentralisation; 
Contributed to design of new $12M UNCDF/UNDP decentralisation & local development support program;
